{"tid":601551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[信邊個？]政府統計處Vs CitiBank調查","createTime":"2018-03-22T10:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T16:45:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"24cdcab306d46fcc2a8779eb4504df21aabc2619","tid":601551,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"政府  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCiti  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處:<br />\n<br />\n長者工作人口增加，按收入來源分析，有職業收入的長者住戶的<span style=\"color: red;\">每月收入中位數由2006年的8,000元增加至2016年的1.2萬元</span>，增幅逾五成；而沒有職業收入的長者住戶每月收入中位數，增幅更明顯，高達8成，由3,200元增加至5,780元，部分原因是受惠於政府現金社會福利。<br />\n<br />\n按長者與各區人口總數的比例分析，觀塘區和黃大仙區的長者佔該區人口的比例最高，均為17.2%，其次是葵青區、南區及東區均約為16%，而荃灣區則為最低，為14.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/166697/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF65%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%8510%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE3%E6%88%90%E8%87%B3116%E8%90%AC-%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD15%E8%90%AC%E7%82%BA%E7%8D%A8%E5%B1%85%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F166697%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF65%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%258510%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2580%25BE3%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%2587%25B3116%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD15%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25B1%2585%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585&d=lGp%2BW%2Fb0xW9AC6B%2ByqwOK%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eccb8411\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/166697/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF65%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%8510%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE3%E6%88%90%E8%87%B3116%E8%90%AC-%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD15%E8%90%AC%E7%82%BA%E7%8D%A8%E5%B1%85%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCitiBank:<br />\n<br />\n2017年港千萬富翁數目達68,000人，按年增加15%，佔人口1%，平均年齡為58歲。<br />\n<br />\n港富豪中5成半<span style=\"color: red;\">主要財富來源來自固定薪酬</span>，只有2成來自以做生意獲利為主要收入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180322/large/1521704420_38bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180322%2Flarge%2F1521704420_38bc.jpg&h=863a7071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180322/57979938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979938&d=lGp%2BW%2Fb0xW9AC6B%2ByqwOK%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d9c428df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979938&h=ef1909fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180322/57979938</a>"},{"pid":"a245aee3d6ab3c87aabe0afd7488bc81edf9f1fd","tid":601551,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96f1aa17d651e1fe6d9e959403711f367248c3b","tid":601551,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"一個係有職業收入的長者住戶<br />\n另一個係千萬富翁<br />\n<br />\n基數唔同點比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fdc6d5465133854e4bd89fb068179d9065b2c6","tid":601551,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"堆富豪係統計學上既Outliers咁滯<br />\n老統用中位數先比較合理"},{"pid":"1e4a5e80d6f2e375a4a8590e005a761e5642a615","tid":601551,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"我只信老貓"},{"pid":"8c2bd53953a8a751e97ce982ea9bcfa723ee96f9","tid":601551,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪